name: untitled 00
description:
Controls: WASD only

once you run out of power  (red bar at the top), you die.

Dirt: a block which you can pick and carry around.

Stone: like dirt, but much harder to carry. you can't jump if you hold it.

Mushroom: eat it to regain power. you have to look for it, and clear out paths to find it.

this is the most basic version of this game. it does not contain other players (yet).

also join https://discord.gg/TS8jy9CmWj to help me grow my community.
